                            <comment id="13835872" author="mps" created="Sat, 30 Nov 2013 19:53:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;When I initially filed this issue, I wasn&apos;t sure whether it should be classified as a bug or and improvement. After reading &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.datastax.com/docs/datastax_enterprise1.0/about_pig&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://www.datastax.com/docs/datastax_enterprise1.0/about_pig&lt;/a&gt;, I think it should be classified as a bug, because the data &lt;tt&gt;B&lt;/tt&gt; in the issue description is in a form that this link says should be suitable for storing into Cassandra.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
